    Form for use in file uploads. For upload of a document as a single chunk, 'first' and 'last' should both be set to TRUE (uploadId is ignored). For chunked upload, send the first part with first=TRUE, then send the returned uploadId from the first part with subsequent parts. The document is parsed when the final part is sent with last=TRUE. Hash should always be set to the md5 hash of the entire document. For chunked upload, the hash is checked against the complete document after the chunks are joined.
